112
00:08:19,650 --> 00:08:20,690
Ya...

113
00:08:21,890 --> 00:08:23,320
Itu bukan karena kamu.

114
00:08:24,729 --> 00:08:26,330
Seiring ayahmu bangkrut

115
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:28,299
dan melarikan diri,

116
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:30,599
itu terjadi begitu saja.

117
00:08:31,299 --> 00:08:32,729
Sebelum aku datang,

118
00:08:33,299 --> 00:08:35,970
kudengar kalian berdua baik-baik saja.

119
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:38,309
Aku masih kecil.

120
00:08:38,809 --> 00:08:40,840
Tapi aku bisa melihat bahwa Ayah baik kepada Ibu.

121
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,880
Moon Sik.

122
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:42,939
Jadi,

123
00:08:44,439 --> 00:08:46,779
