Aku sebaiknya pergi ke kantor sekarang.

144
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,520
Baik.

145
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:13,730
Halo, Hyo Seob.

146
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:16,470
Sekarang?

147
00:10:31,789 --> 00:10:33,449
Park Hyo Seob tidak mau memberi tahu Ibu

148
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:36,760
