149
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,429
Walaupun

150
00:10:39,959 --> 00:10:42,529
dia akan memberi tahu ibuku,

151
00:10:43,829 --> 00:10:47,230
apakah Ibu akan memercayai dia

152
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:49,740
atau aku?

153
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:23,000
Sedang apa di sini?

154
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,939
Kenapa?

155
00:11:25,610 --> 00:11:27,140
Kamu merindukanku?

156
00:11:28,010 --> 00:11:29,179
Ya...

157
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:33,179
Aku hanya memikirkanmu.

158
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:37,890
Kamu pasti kasihan kepadaku.

159
00:11:44,459 --> 00:11:46,189
Soal Moon Sik, Mi Yeon.

160
00:11:46,730 --> 00:11:47,730
Ya.

161
00:11:49,659 --> 00:11:51,230
Apa dia punya

162
