168
00:12:09,819 --> 00:12:10,949
Tidak.

169
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:13,319
Moon Sik menyukaimu.

170
00:12:16,319 --> 00:12:18,760
Dia hanya ingin kasih sayang seorang ayah.

171
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:21,630
Dia kira

172
