236
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,730
Kakak akan bunuh diri di sini jika begitu.

237
00:16:50,029 --> 00:16:54,429
Astaga, kamu mulai lagi.

238
00:16:54,669 --> 00:16:57,640
